66.5	Simon_Singh	Simon Singh	Simon Lehna Singh, MBE (born 1 January 1964) is a British author who has specialised in writing about mathematical and scientific topics in an accessible manner. His written works include Fermat's Last Theorem (in the United States titled Fermat's Enigma: The Epic Quest to Solve the World's Greatest Mathematical Problem), The Code Book (about cryptography and its history), Big Bang (about the Big Bang theory and the origins of the universe) and Trick or Treatment? Alternative Medicine on Trial (about complementary and alternative medicine).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5e/Simon_Singh_TAM_London_2009.jpg/220px-Simon_Singh_TAM_London_2009.jpg
